{"tid":674634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指性別歧視   佐丹撤回新系列廣告","createTime":"2018-05-23T01:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T08:16:00.000Z","uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"50bf7790cc0b64b5fafb738d2c32d8d5398b96fd","tid":674634,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn3.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/700x400/public/images/methode/2018/05/22/91aa247e-5d70-11e8-a4de-9f5e0e4dd719_1280x720_183427.PNG?itok=OTKJvykO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn3.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F700x400%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F91aa247e-5d70-11e8-a4de-9f5e0e4dd719_1280x720_183427.PNG%3Fitok%3DOTKJvykO&h=d9d3b92a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/images/methode/2018/05/22/11f458ce-5d77-11e8-a4de-9f5e0e4dd719_972x_183427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F11f458ce-5d77-11e8-a4de-9f5e0e4dd719_972x_183427.jpg&h=f4130c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHong Kong fashion brand Giordano has been forced to remove what has been described as a &ldquo;sexist&rdquo; advertising campaign for a new clothing line after mounting public outcry on social media.<br />\n<br />\nThe &ldquo;Team Family Series&rdquo; advert shows a family posing together with the wife wearing a T-shirt emblazoned with the word &ldquo;Cook&rdquo;, while the man&rsquo;s shirt reads &ldquo;Work&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nThe advert posted on social media last week has drawn fire online from dozens of outraged users, with some threatening to boycott the store because of the &ldquo;sexist&rdquo; image.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This ad is an absolute disgrace Giordano,&rdquo; one user wrote. &ldquo;Unforgivable for a modern brand to stereotype men and women in such an awful way. Shame on you and get a grip &ndash; it&rsquo;s 2018, not the 1950s.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAnother user wrote: &ldquo;I just had to unshackle myself from the kitchen and break from my &lsquo;cooking&rsquo; duties to let you know that the 1950s called, they want their attitudes back. How on earth do you call this &lsquo;family time&rsquo;? Absolutely disgraceful. Shame on you! #notmyfamily.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.scmp.com/lifestyle/fashion-beauty/article/2147224/hong-kong-fashion-brand-giordino-remove-sexist-ad-after\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.scmp.com%2Flifestyle%2Ffashion-beauty%2Farticle%2F2147224%2Fhong-kong-fashion-brand-giordino-remove-sexist-ad-after&d=K6p3p5RThtSZ1kxDxcZNDtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ccdd11ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.scmp.com/lifestyle/fashion-beauty/article/2147224/hong-kong-fashion-brand-giordino-remove-sexist-ad-after</a>"},{"pid":"d4f414871fef3e572cd5d55b9905a9538672406a","tid":674634,"uid":389,"like":222,"dislike":15,"score":207,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:04:01.000Z","msg":"平權撚真係痴鳩線"},{"pid":"71a757bd585b4aee85d523d3e03e06c644cb98ee","tid":674634,"uid":55851,"like":149,"dislike":6,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:04:10.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講：女權撚話女人著Cook等於性別定形，所以屌鳩佐丹奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0afc2c9282ec9c2b1538cd7f2bef6c5b3e90d22","tid":674634,"uid":1988,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"我果日睇到都嚇左一跳<br />\n實俾女權插啦"},{"pid":"ac34d2d2cf5d89744327bbea3e64389ae6514ed7","tid":674634,"uid":118973,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:07:53.000Z","msg":"乜L嘢佐丹<br />\n<br />\n左手丹我就識"},{"pid":"e45efd1aec2f92ae8621cae9ac57bcb35cf28cb6","tid":674634,"uid":28599,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"應該搵個女人著一件寫住Bitch既衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{